  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking an experienced and results-driven Sales\nManager to lead our sales operations, drive revenue growth, and expand market\npresence. The ideal candidate will be responsible for developing sales\nstrategies, managing and motivating the sales team, building strong client\nrelationships, and ensuring the achievement of company targets.</p><p><strong>Key Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and implement effective sales strategies to achieve\nrevenue and growth targets</li><li>Lead, supervise, and motivate the sales team to improve\nperformance and productivity</li><li>Identify new business opportunities, markets, and potential\nclients</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with key customers\nand business partners</li><li>Set sales targets, monitor performance, and prepare regular\nsales reports for management</li><li>Negotiate contracts, pricing, and commercial terms to\nmaximize profitability</li><li>Coordinate with marketing, operations, and finance teams to\nensure smooth order execution</li><li>Analyze market trends, customer feedback, and competitor\nactivities to support strategic decision-making</li><li>Ensure high levels of customer satisfaction and handle\nescalations or major complaints professionally</li><li>Train, coach, and evaluate sales staff to enhance skills and\ncareer development</li><li>Manage sales budgets and monitor expenses effectively</li><li>Ensure compliance with company policies, procedures, and\nlegal requirements</li></ul><p><strong>Education & Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree in any discipline</li></ul><p><strong>Experience Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum <strong>5–7 years</strong> of experience in sales, business\ndevelopment, or account management</li><li>Proven experience in leading and managing a sales team</li><li>Strong track record of achieving sales targets and driving\nbusiness growth</li><li>Prior experience in <strong>trading, import-export, or\nservice-based industries</strong> is an advantage</li></ul><ul><li>Good understanding of market analysis, customer relationship\nmanagement, and negotiation techniques</li></ul><p><strong>Skills & Competencies:</strong></p><ul><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Strong leadership and people management abilities</li><li>Ability to work independently and perform under pressure</li><li>Proficient in <strong>MS Office applications</strong> and <strong>CRM\nsystems</strong></li><li>Strong analytical, problem-solving, and decision-making\nskills</li></ul>",
